{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775869112505,"sessionID":"ses_285f4a69fffebISu6m4ck4XKHy","part":{"id":"prt_d7a0c3095001KOQ7OfR7Kee15U","messageID":"msg_d7a0c2601001snkuS1dTb1sCBV","sessionID":"ses_285f4a69fffebISu6m4ck4XKHy","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-2785bd64d120481986fbcf41a9e56a89","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-022: CLI publish 命令\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: 实现 AgentCube CLI 的 `publish` 命令，用于将构建好的容器镜像发布到 Kubernetes 集群。该命令支持两种发布方式：AgentCube 自定义资源（AgentRuntime CR）和标准 Kubernetes 资源（Deployment + Service），能够处理镜像推送、资源部署和元数据更新。\n6: \n7: ## Purpose\n8: \n9: 提供 `kubectl-agentcube publish` 命令，实现：\n10: \n11: 1. **镜像准备**：支持本地镜像推送到容器注册表，或使用云端构建的镜像 URL\n12: 2. **AgentCube 提供商**：部署到 AgentRuntime 自定义资源，集成工作负载管理器和路由器\n13: 3. **标准 K8s 提供商**：部署到标准的 Deployment 和 NodePort Service\n14: 4. **版本管理**：支持语义化版本号，更新元数据中的部署信息\n15: 5. **部署配置**：支持命名空间、副本数、节点端口等配置\n16: 6. **状态验证**：等待部署就绪，提供详细的部署状态反馈\n17: \n18: ## Module\n19: \n20: `cmd/cli` - AgentCube CLI 工具包\n21: \n22: ## Language\n23: \n24: Python 3.10+\n25: \n26: ## Size\n27: \n28: L\n29: \n30: ## Scope\n31: \n32: ### In Scope\n33: \n34: 1. **PublishRuntime 类实现** (`agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py`)\n35:    - `publish()` 主方法，支持两种提供商\n36:    - `_publish_cr_to_k8s()` - AgentRuntime CR 部署\n37:    - `_publish_k8s()` - 标准 K8s 资源部署\n38:    - `_prepare_image_for_publishing()` - 镜像准备\n39:    - `_prepare_local_image()` - 本地镜像推送\n40:    - `_prepare_cloud_image()` - 云端镜像验证\n41:    - `_update_publish_metadata()` - 更新发布元数据\n42: \n43: 2. **CLI 命令集成** (`agentcube/cli/main.py`)\n44:    - `publish()` Typer 命令函数\n45:    - 命令行参数：`--workspace`, `--version`, `--image-url`, `--provider`, `--namespace`, `--replicas`, `--node-port`, `--region`, `--cloud-provider`, `--description`, `--verbose`\n46:    - 错误处理和用户反馈\n47: \n48: 3. **AgentCube 提供商** (`agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py`)\n49:    - `deploy_agent_runtime()` - 部署 AgentRuntime CR\n50:    - 设置默认会话超时\n51:    - 配置工作负载管理器和路由器 URL\n52: \n53: 4. **Kubernetes 提供商** (`agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py`)\n54:    - `deploy_agent()` - 部署 Deployment 和 Service\n55:    - `wait_for_deployment_ready()` - 等待部署就绪\n56:    - 支持节点端口配置\n57: \n58: 5. **Docker 服务集成** (`agentcube/services/docker_service.py`)\n59:    - `push_image()` - 推送镜像到注册表\n60:    - 镜像标记和凭证管理\n61: \n62: 6. **元数据服务集成** (`agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`)\n63:    - 加载和保存 `agent_metadata.yaml`\n64:    - 部署信息持久化\n65: \n66: ### Out of Scope\n67: \n68: - 容器注册表管理（使用已有服务）\n69: - Kubernetes 集群安装和配置\n70: - 镜像构建功能（由 `build` 命令完成）\n71: - 工作空间打包功能（由 `pack` 命令完成）\n72: \n73: ## Impact Analysis\n74: \n75: ### Components Impacted\n76: \n77: 1. **CLI 工具包** (`cmd/cli`)\n78:    - 添加 `publish` 命令到 Typer 应用\n79:    - 新增 `PublishRuntime` 类\n80:    - 更新导入和依赖\n81: \n82: 2. **Kubernetes 客户端**\n83:    - 集成 `kubernetes` Python 客户端库\n84:    - 支持 AgentRuntime CRD 操作\n85:    - 支持标准 K8s 资源操作\n86: \n87: 3. **Docker 服务**\n88:    - 确保已实现 `push_image()` 方法\n89:    - 支持镜像标记和推送\n90: \n91: 4. **提供商服务**\n92:    - `AgentCubeProvider` 用于 AgentRuntime CR 部署\n93:    - `KubernetesProvider` 用于标准 K8s 部署\n94: \n95: 5. **用户工作流**\n96:    - `pack` → `build` → `publish` → `invoke` 的完整链路\n97:    - 元数据文件在命令间传递状态\n98: \n99: ### Dependencies\n100: \n101: **核心依赖**（已在 `pyproject.toml` 中定义）：\n102: - `typer[all]>=0.9.0` - CLI 框架\n103: - `pydantic>=2.0.0` - 数据验证\n104: - `pyyaml>=6.0` - YAML 解析\n105: - `docker>=6.0.0` - Docker SDK\n106: - `rich>=13.0.0` - 美化输出\n107: - `kubernetes>=28.0.0` - Kubernetes 客户端\n108: \n109: **可选依赖**：\n110: - `httpx>=0.24.0` - HTTP 客户端\n111: \n112: ### Security Considerations\n113: \n114: 1. **镜像凭证安全**\n115:    - 支持安全的镜像注册表认证（HTTPS）\n116:    - 避免在日志中输出凭证\n117:    - 支持凭证轮换\n118: \n119: 2. **Kubernetes 访问安全**\n120:    - 验证 kubeconfig 配置\n121:    - 支持命名空间隔离\n122:    - 避免权限提升\n123: \n124: 3. **元数据安全**\n125:    - 避免在元数据中存储敏感信息\n126:    - 确保文件权限正确\n127:    - 支持元数据加密（可选）\n128: \n129: 4. **部署安全**\n130:    - 验证镜像来源\n131:    - 支持镜像签名验证（可选）\n132:    - 限制资源使用\n133: \n134: ## Design Decisions\n135: \n136: ### 提供商选择策略\n137: \n138: **选择**：支持 AgentCube（AgentRuntime CR）和标准 K8s（Deployment + Service）两种提供商\n139: \n140: **理由**：\n141: - AgentCube 提供商：利用 AgentCube 特性（会话管理、工作负载管理器、路由器）\n142: - 标准 K8s 提供商：兼容标准 Kubernetes 集群\n143: - 满足不同部署场景需求\n144: \n145: **实现**：\n146: ```python\n147: if provider == \"agentcube\":\n148:     result = self._publish_cr_to_k8s(workspace_path, metadata, **options)\n149: elif provider == \"k8s\":\n150:     result = self._publish_k8s(workspace_path, metadata, **options)\n151: else:\n152:     raise ValueError(f\"Unsupported provider: {provider}\")\n153: ```\n154: \n155: ### 镜像准备策略\n156: \n157: **选择**：根据构建模式选择镜像准备方式\n158: \n159: **理由**：\n160: - 本地构建模式：需要推送镜像到注册表\n161: - 云端构建模式：直接使用云端镜像 URL\n162: - 灵活支持不同构建场景\n163: \n164: **实现**：\n165: ```python\n166: def _prepare_image_for_publishing(\n167:     self,\n168:     workspace_path: Path,\n169:     metadata,\n170:     options: Dict[str, Any]\n171: ) -> str:\n172:     \"\"\"Prepare image for publishing.\"\"\"\n173:     build_mode = metadata.build_mode or \"local\"\n174: \n175:     if build_mode == \"local\":\n176:         return self._prepare_local_image(workspace_path, metadata, options)\n177:     elif build_mode == \"cloud\":\n178:         return self._prepare_cloud_image(workspace_path, metadata, options)\n179:     else:\n180:         raise ValueError(f\"Unsupported build mode: {build_mode}\")\n181: ```\n182: \n183: ### 版本管理策略\n184: \n185: **选择**：使用语义化版本号，支持版本覆盖\n186: \n187: **理由**：\n188: - 符合软件版本管理最佳实践\n189: - 便于版本追踪和回滚\n190: - 支持多版本并存\n191: \n192: **实现**：\n193: ```python\n194: version = options.get(\"version\") or metadata.version\n195: if not version:\n196:     raise ValueError(\"Version must be specified either via --version or in metadata\")\n197: \n198: # 更新元数据中的版本\n199: metadata.version = version\n200: self.metadata_service.save_metadata(workspace_path, metadata)\n201: ```\n202: \n203: ### 部署验证策略\n204: \n205: **选择**：等待部署就绪，提供实时状态反馈\n206: \n207: **理由**：\n208: - 确保部署成功后才返回\n209: - 提供用户友好的进度反馈\n210: - 便于问题诊断\n211: \n212: **实现**：\n213: ```python\n214: # 等待部署就绪\n215: if provider == \"k8s\":\n216:     k8s_provider = KubernetesProvider(\n217:         namespace=namespace,\n218:         verbose=self.verbose\n219:     )\n220:     k8s_provider.wait_for_deployment_ready(\n221:         deployment_name,\n222:         timeout=120\n223:     )\n224: ```\n225: \n226: ## Alternatives Considered\n227: \n228: ### Alternative 1: 仅支持 AgentCube 提供商\n229: \n230: **描述**：仅支持 AgentRuntime CR 部署，不支持标准 K8s 资源\n231: \n232: **优点**：\n233: - 实现简单\n234: - 充分利用 AgentCube 特性\n235: - 统一的部署体验\n236: \n237: **缺点**：\n238: - 不兼容标准 Kubernetes 集群\n239: - 限制部署场景\n240: - 增加用户迁移成本\n241: \n242: **选择**：不采纳 - 需要支持标准 K8s 以提高兼容性\n243: \n244: ### Alternative 2: 不支持镜像推送\n245: \n246: **描述**：仅支持使用云端镜像 URL，不支持本地镜像推送\n247: \n248: **优点**：\n249: - 实现简单\n250: - 避免镜像管理复杂性\n251: \n252: **缺点**：\n253: - 无法满足本地构建需求\n254: - 增加部署成本\n255: - 限制灵活性\n256: \n257: **选择**：不采纳 - 镜像推送是本地构建的必要功能\n258: \n259: ### Alternative 3: 不等待部署就绪\n260: \n261: **描述**：提交部署请求后立即返回，不等待部署就绪\n262: \n263: **优点**：\n264: - 响应速度快\n265: - 实现简单\n266: \n267: **缺点**：\n268: - 无法确认部署成功\n269: - 错误诊断困难\n270: - 用户体验差\n271: \n272: **选择**：不采纳 - 等待部署就绪是必要的\n273: \n274: ## Implementation Plan\n275: \n276: ### Phase 1: PublishRuntime 基础框架 (Day 1-2)\n277: \n278: 1. 创建 `agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py` 文件\n279: 2. 实现 `PublishRuntime` 类基础结构\n280: 3. 实现 `__init__` 方法\n281: 4. 实现 `publish()` 方法框架\n282: \n283: **代码框架**：\n284: ```python\n285: from pathlib import Path\n286: from typing import Any, Dict, Optional\n287: import logging\n288: \n289: from agentcube.services.docker_service import DockerService\n290: from agentcube.services.metadata_service import MetadataService\n291: from agentcube.services.agentcube_provider import AgentCubeProvider\n292: from agentcube.services.k8s_provider import KubernetesProvider\n293: \n294: logger = logging.getLogger(__name__)\n295: \n296: class PublishRuntime:\n297:     def __init__(self, verbose: bool = False, provider: str = \"agentcube\") -> None:\n298:         self.verbose = verbose\n299:         self.provider = provider\n300:         self.docker_service = DockerService(verbose=verbose)\n301:         self.metadata_service = MetadataService(verbose=verbose)\n302: \n303:     def publish(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n304:         \"\"\"Publish agent to Kubernetes.\"\"\"\n305:         # 实现发布逻辑\n306:         pass\n307: ```\n308: \n309: ### Phase 2: 镜像准备实现 (Day 2-3)\n310: \n311: 1. 实现 `_prepare_image_for_publishing()` 方法\n312: 2. 实现 `_prepare_local_image()` 方法\n313: 3. 实现 `_prepare_cloud_image()` 方法\n314: \n315: **实现**：\n316: ```python\n317: def _prepare_image_for_publishing(\n318:     self,\n319:     workspace_path: Path,\n320:     metadata,\n321:     options: Dict[str, Any]\n322: ) -> str:\n323:     \"\"\"Prepare image for publishing.\"\"\"\n324:     build_mode = metadata.build_mode or \"local\"\n325: \n326:     if self.verbose:\n327:         logger.info(f\"Preparing image for {build_mode} build mode\")\n328: \n329:     if build_mode == \"local\":\n330:         return self._prepare_local_image(workspace_path, metadata, options)\n331:     elif build_mode == \"cloud\":\n332:         return self._prepare_cloud_image(workspace_path, metadata, options)\n333:     else:\n334:         raise ValueError(f\"Unsupported build mode: {build_mode}\")\n335: \n336: def _prepare_local_image(\n337:     self,\n338:     workspace_path: Path,\n339:     metadata,\n340:     options: Dict[str, Any]\n341: ) -> str:\n342:     \"\"\"Prepare local image by pushing to registry.\"\"\"\n343:     # 获取镜像信息\n344:     image_info = metadata.image\n345:     if not image_info:\n346:         raise ValueError(\"No image information found in metadata\")\n347: \n348:     image_name = image_info.get(\"name\")\n349:     tag = metadata.version or image_info.get(\"tag\", \"latest\")\n350: \n351:     # 检查是否需要推送到注册表\n352:     image_url = options.get(\"image_url\")\n353:     registry_url = metadata.registry_url or \"\"\n354: \n355:     if not registry_url and not image_url:\n356:         raise ValueError(\n357:             \"Image URL must be specified via --image-url for local build mode, \"\n358:             \"or registry_url must be set in agent_metadata.yaml\"\n359:         )\n360: \n361:     # 构建完整的镜像 URL\n362:     full_image_url = image_url or f\"{registry_url}/{image_name}:{tag}\"\n363: \n364:     if self.verbose:\n365:         logger.info(f\"Pushing image to registry: {full_image_url}\")\n366: \n367:     # 推送镜像\n368:     push_result = self.docker_service.push_image(\n369:         image_name=image_name,\n370:         tag=tag,\n371:         registry_url=registry_url,\n372:         username=options.get(\"image_username\") or metadata.registry_username,\n373:         password=options.get(\"image_password\") or metadata.registry_password\n374:     )\n375: \n376:     if self.verbose:\n377:         logger.info(f\"Image pushed successfully: {push_result}\")\n378: \n379:     return full_image_url\n380: \n381: def _prepare_cloud_image(\n382:     self,\n383:     workspace_path: Path,\n384:     metadata,\n385:     options: Dict[str, Any]\n386: ) -> str:\n387:     \"\"\"Prepare cloud image URL.\"\"\"\n388:     image_url = options.get(\"image_url\")\n389: \n390:     if not image_url:\n391:         raise ValueError(\n392:             \"Image URL must be specified via --image-url for cloud build mode\"\n393:         )\n394: \n395:     if self.verbose:\n396:         logger.info(f\"Using cloud image URL: {image_url}\")\n397: \n398:     return image_url\n399: ```\n400: \n401: ### Phase 3: AgentCube 提供商实现 (Day 3-4)\n402: \n403: 1. 实现 `_publish_cr_to_k8s()` 方法\n404: 2. 验证前置条件\n405: 3. 调用 AgentCubeProvider 部署\n406: 4. 更新元数据\n407: \n408: **实现**：\n409: ```python\n410: def _publish_cr_to_k8s(\n411:     self,\n412:     workspace_path: Path,\n413:     metadata,\n414:     **options: Any\n415: ) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n416:     \"\"\"Publish using AgentRuntime CR.\"\"\"\n417:     # 验证前置条件\n418:     if not metadata.router_url:\n419:         raise ValueError(\n420:             \"router_url is required in agent_metadata.yaml for agentcube provider\"\n421:         )\n422:     if not metadata.workload_manager_url:\n423:         raise ValueError(\n424:             \"workload_manager_url is required in agent_metadata.yaml for agentcube provider\"\n425:         )\n426: \n427:     # 准备镜像 URL\n428:     image_url = self._prepare_image_for_publishing(\n429:         workspace_path, metadata, options\n430:     )\n431: \n432:     if self.verbose:\n433:         logger.info(\"Deploying to AgentCube provider...\")\n434: \n435:     # 创建 AgentCubeProvider\n436:     namespace = options.get(\"namespace\") or \"default\"\n437:     agentcube_provider = AgentCubeProvider(\n438:         namespace=namespace,\n439:         verbose=self.verbose\n440:     )\n441: \n442:     # 部署 AgentRuntime CR\n443:     deploy_result = agentcube_provider.deploy_agent_runtime(\n444:         agent_name=metadata.agent_name,\n445:         image_url=image_url,\n446:         port=metadata.port,\n447:         entrypoint=metadata.entrypoint,\n448:         env_vars=None,\n449:         workload_manager_url=metadata.workload_manager_url,\n450:         router_url=metadata.router_url,\n451:         readiness_probe_path=metadata.readiness_probe_path,\n452:         readiness_probe_port=metadata.readiness_probe_port\n453:     )\n454: \n455:     if self.verbose:\n456:         logger.info(f\"AgentRuntime CR deployed: {deploy_result}\")\n457: \n458:     # 更新元数据\n459:     agent_info = {\n460:         \"agent_id\": deploy_result.get(\"agent_id\"),\n461:         \"agent_endpoint\": deploy_result.get(\"agent_endpoint\"),\n462:         \"deployment_type\": \"AgentRuntime\",\n463:         \"namespace\": namespace\n464:     }\n465: \n466:     self._update_publish_metadata(workspace_path, agent_info)\n467: \n468:     return deploy_result\n469: ```\n470: \n471: ### Phase 4: K8s 提供商实现 (Day 4-5)\n472: \n473: 1. 实现 `_publish_k8s()` 方法\n474: 2. 验证前置条件\n475: 3. 调用 KubernetesProvider 部署\n476: 4. 等待部署就绪\n477: 5. 更新元数据\n478: \n479: **实现**：\n480: ```python\n481: def _publish_k8s(\n482:     self,\n483:     workspace_path: Path,\n484:     metadata,\n485:     **options: Any\n486: ) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n487:     \"\"\"Publish using standard K8s resources.\"\"\"\n488:     # 准备镜像 URL\n489:     image_url = self._prepare_image_for_publishing(\n490:         workspace_path, metadata, options\n491:     )\n492: \n493:     if self.verbose:\n494:         logger.info(\"Deploying to Kubernetes provider...\")\n495: \n496:     # 创建 KubernetesProvider\n497:     namespace = options.get(\"namespace\") or \"default\"\n498:     k8s_provider = KubernetesProvider(\n499:         namespace=namespace,\n500:         verbose=self.verbose\n501:     )\n502: \n503:     # 部署 Deployment 和 Service\n504:     deploy_result = k8s_provider.deploy_agent(\n505:         agent_name=metadata.agent_name,\n506:         image_url=image_url,\n507:         port=metadata.port,\n508:         entrypoint=metadata.entrypoint,\n509:         replicas=options.get(\"replicas\", 1),\n510:         node_port=options.get(\"node_port\"),\n511:         env_vars=None\n512:     )\n513: \n514:     if self.verbose:\n515:         logger.info(f\"K8s resources created: {deploy_result}\")\n516: \n517:     # 等待部署就绪\n518:     deployment_name = deploy_result.get(\"deployment_name\")\n519:     try:\n520:         k8s_provider.wait_for_deployment_ready(\n521:             deployment_name,\n522:             timeout=120\n523:         )\n524:         if self.verbose:\n525:             logger.info(f\"Deployment {deployment_name} is ready\")\n526:     except TimeoutError as e:\n527:         error_msg = f\"Deployment {deployment_name} failed to become ready within timeout\"\n528:         logger.error(error_msg)\n529:         # 更新元数据记录错误\n530:         agent_info = {\n531:             \"deployment_type\": \"K8s\",\n532:             \"namespace\": namespace,\n533:             \"status\": \"error\",\n534:             \"error\": str(e)\n535:         }\n536:         self._update_publish_metadata(workspace_path, agent_info)\n537:         raise RuntimeError(error_msg) from e\n538: \n539:     # 更新元数据\n540:     agent_info = {\n541:         \"deployment_type\": \"K8s\",\n542:         \"namespace\": namespace,\n543:         \"deployment_name\": deploy_result.get(\"deployment_name\"),\n544:         \"service_name\": deploy_result.get(\"service_name\"),\n545:         \"service_url\": deploy_result.get(\"service_url\"),\n546:         \"node_port\": deploy_result.get(\"node_port\"),\n547:         \"replicas\": deploy_result.get(\"replicas\"),\n548:         \"status\": \"deployed\"\n549:     }\n550: \n551:     self._update_publish_metadata(workspace_path, agent_info)\n552: \n553:     return deploy_result\n554: ```\n555: \n556: ### Phase 5: 元数据更新实现 (Day 5)\n557: \n558: 1. 实现 `_update_publish_metadata()` 方法\n559: 2. 更新部署信息\n560: 3. 持久化元数据\n561: \n562: **实现**：\n563: ```python\n564: def _update_publish_metadata(\n565:     self,\n566:     workspace_path: Path,\n567:     agent_info: Dict[str, Any]\n568: ) -> None:\n569:     \"\"\"Update metadata with publish information.\"\"\"\n570:     # 加载元数据\n571:     metadata = self.metadata_service.load_metadata(workspace_path)\n572: \n573:     # 更新部署信息\n574:     metadata.k8s_deployment = agent_info\n575:     if \"agent_id\" in agent_info:\n576:         metadata.agent_id = agent_info[\"agent_id\"]\n577:     if \"agent_endpoint\" in agent_info:\n578:         metadata.agent_endpoint = agent_info[\"agent_endpoint\"]\n579: \n580:     # 保存元数据\n581:     self.metadata_service.save_metadata(workspace_path, metadata)\n582: \n583:     if self.verbose:\n584:         logger.info(f\"Metadata updated with publish info: {agent_info}\")\n585: ```\n586: \n587: ### Phase 6: CLI 命令集成 (Day 5-6)\n588: \n589: 1. 在 `agentcube/cli/main.py` 中添加 `publish` 命令\n590: 2. 添加命令行参数\n591: 3. 集成 PublishRuntime\n592: 4. 实现错误处理和 Rich 输出\n593: \n594: **实现**：\n595: ```python\n596: import typer\n597: from pathlib import Path\n598: from typing import Optional, List\n599: from rich.console import Console\n600: from rich.table import Table\n601: \n602: from agentcube.runtime.publish_runtime import PublishRuntime\n603: \n604: def publish(\n605:     workspace: str = typer.Option(\n606:         \".\", \"-f\", \"--workspace\",\n607:         help=\"Path to the agent workspace directory\",\n608:         show_default=True\n609:     ),\n610:     version: Optional[str] = typer.Option(\n611:         None, \"--version\",\n612:         help=\"Semantic version string (e.g., v1.0.0)\"\n613:     ),\n614:     image_url: Optional[str] = typer.Option(\n615:         None, \"--image-url\",\n616:         help=\"Image repository URL (required in local build mode)\"\n617:     ),\n618:     image_username: Optional[str] = typer.Option(\n619:         None, \"--image-username\",\n620:         help=\"Username for image repository\"\n621:     ),\n622:     image_password: Optional[str] = typer.Option(\n623:         None, \"--image-password\",\n624:         help=\"Password for image repository\"\n625:     ),\n626:     description: Optional[str] = typer.Option(\n627:         None, \"--description\",\n628:         help=\"Agent description\"\n629:     ),\n630:     region: Optional[str] = typer.Option(\n631:         None, \"--region\",\n632:         help=\"Deployment region\"\n633:     ),\n634:     cloud_provider: Optional[str] = typer.Option(\n635:         None, \"--cloud-provider\",\n636:         help=\"Cloud provider name (e.g., huawei)\"\n637:     ),\n638:     provider: str = typer.Option(\n639:         \"agentcube\", \"--provider\",\n640:         help=\"Target provider: 'agentcube' (AgentRuntime CR) or 'k8s' (Deployment/Service)\"\n641:     ),\n642:     node_port: Optional[int] = typer.Option(\n643:         None, \"--node-port\",\n644:         help=\"Specific NodePort to use (30000-32767) for K8s deployment\"\n645:     ),\n646:     replicas: Optional[int] = typer.Option(\n647:         None, \"--replicas\",\n648:         help=\"Number of replicas for K8s deployment (default: 1)\"\n649:     ),\n650:     namespace: Optional[str] = typer.Option(\n651:         None, \"--namespace\",\n652:         help=\"The namespace for the deployment\"\n653:     ),\n654:     verbose: bool = typer.Option(\n655:         False, \"--verbose\",\n656:         help=\"Enable detailed logging\"\n657:     )\n658: ) -> None:\n659:     \"\"\"Publish agent to Kubernetes.\"\"\"\n660:     workspace_path = Path(workspace)\n661: \n662:     try:\n663:         runtime = PublishRuntime(verbose=verbose, provider=provider)\n664: \n665:         # 准备选项\n666:         options = {\n667:             \"version\": version,\n668:             \"image_url\": image_url,\n669:             \"image_username\": image_username,\n670:             \"image_password\": image_password,\n671:             \"description\": description,\n672:             \"region\": region,\n673:             \"cloud_provider\": cloud_provider,\n674:             \"provider\": provider,\n675:             \"node_port\": node_port,\n676:             \"replicas\": replicas,\n677:             \"namespace\": namespace\n678:         }\n679: \n680:         # 执行发布\n681:         result = runtime.publish(workspace_path=workspace_path, **options)\n682: \n683:         # 输出成功信息\n684:         console = Console()\n685:         console.print(\"[green]✓[/green] Agent published successfully!\")\n686: \n687:         # 创建结果表格\n688:         table = Table(title=\"Deployment Information\")\n689:         table.add_column(\"Field\", style=\"cyan\")\n690:         table.add_column(\"Value\", style=\"green\")\n691: \n692:         table.add_row(\"Provider\", provider)\n693:         table.add_row(\"Agent Name\", result.get(\"agent_name\", \"\"))\n694:         table.add_row(\"Namespace\", result.get(\"namespace\", \"\"))\n695: \n696:         if provider == \"agentcube\":\n697:             table.add_row(\"Agent ID\", result.get(\"agent_id\", \"\"))\n698:             table.add_row(\"Endpoint\", result.get(\"agent_endpoint\", \"\"))\n699:         else:\n700:             table.add_row(\"Deployment\", result.get(\"deployment_name\", \"\"))\n701:             table.add_row(\"Service\", result.get(\"service_name\", \"\"))\n702:             table.add_row(\"Service URL\", result.get(\"service_url\", \"\"))\n703:             if result.get(\"node_port\"):\n704:                 table.add_row(\"Node Port\", str(result.get(\"node_port\")))\n705: \n706:         console.print(table)\n707: \n708:     except Exception as e:\n709:         _handle_error(e, \"publish\", verbose)\n710: ```\n711: \n712: ### Phase 7: 提供商服务完善 (Day 6-7)\n713: \n714: 1. 完善 `AgentCubeProvider.deploy_agent_runtime()` 方法\n715: 2. 完善 `KubernetesProvider.deploy_agent()` 方法\n716: 3. 添加必要的错误处理\n717: \n718: **AgentCubeProvider 实现**：\n719: ```python\n720: def deploy_agent_runtime(\n721:     self,\n722:     agent_name: str,\n723:     image_url: str,\n724:     port: int,\n725:     entrypoint: Optional[str] = None,\n726:     env_vars: Optional[Dict[str, str]] = None,\n727:     workload_manager_url: Optional[str] = None,\n728:     router_url: Optional[str] = None,\n729:     readiness_probe_path: Optional[str] = None,\n730:     readiness_probe_port: Optional[int] = None\n731: ) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n732:     \"\"\"Deploy agent using AgentRuntime CR.\"\"\"\n733:     # 创建 CR 规范\n734:     cr_spec = {\n735:         \"apiVersion\": \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1\",\n736:         \"kind\": \"AgentRuntime\",\n737:         \"metadata\": {\n738:             \"name\": self._sanitize_name(agent_name),\n739:             \"namespace\": self.namespace\n740:         },\n741:         \"spec\": {\n742:             \"image\": image_url,\n743:             \"port\": port,\n744:             \"entrypoint\": entrypoint,\n745:             \"env\": env_vars or {},\n746:             \"sessionTimeout\": \"15m\",\n747:             \"maxSessionDuration\": \"8h\",\n748:             \"readinessProbe\": {\n749:                 \"path\": readiness_probe_path or \"/health\",\n750:                 \"port\": readiness_probe_port or port\n751:             }\n752:         }\n753:     }\n754: \n755:     # 嵌入工作负载管理器和路由器 URL\n756:     if workload_manager_url:\n757:         cr_spec[\"spec\"][\"env\"][\"WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL\"] = workload_manager_url\n758:     if router_url:\n759:         cr_spec[\"spec\"][\"env\"][\"ROUTER_URL\"] = router_url\n760: \n761:     # 添加 imagePullSecrets\n762:     cr_spec[\"spec\"][\"imagePullSecrets\"] = [{\"name\": \"default-secret\"}]\n763: \n764:     if self.verbose:\n765:         logger.info(f\"Creating AgentRuntime CR: {cr_spec}\")\n766: \n767:     # 使用 Kubernetes 客户端创建 CR\n768:     # TODO: 实现 CR 创建逻辑\n769:     pass\n770: \n771:     return {\n772:         \"agent_id\": cr_spec[\"metadata\"][\"name\"],\n773:         \"agent_endpoint\": f\"http://{cr_spec['metadata']['name']}.{self.namespace}.svc.cluster.local:{port}\",\n774:         \"namespace\": self.namespace\n775:     }\n776: ```\n777: \n778: ### Phase 8: 错误处理和验证 (Day 7-8)\n779: \n780: 1. 实现详细的错误信息\n781: 2. 添加输入验证\n782: 3. 实现日志记录\n783: \n784: **验证逻辑**：\n785: ```python\n786: def publish(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n787:     \"\"\"Publish agent to Kubernetes.\"\"\"\n788:     # 加载元数据\n789:     metadata = self.metadata_service.load_metadata(workspace_path)\n790: \n791:     # 验证版本\n792:     version = options.get(\"version\") or metadata.version\n793:     if not version:\n794:         raise ValueError(\n795:             \"Version must be specified either via --version or in metadata\"\n796:         )\n797: \n798:     # 更新元数据版本\n799:     metadata.version = version\n800:     self.metadata_service.save_metadata(workspace_path, metadata)\n801: \n802:     # 根据提供商选择部署方式\n803:     provider = options.get(\"provider\", self.provider)\n804: \n805:     if provider == \"agentcube\":\n806:         return self._publish_cr_to_k8s(workspace_path, metadata, **options)\n807:     elif provider == \"k8s\":\n808:         return self._publish_k8s(workspace_path, metadata, **options)\n809:     else:\n810:         raise ValueError(f\"Unsupported provider: {provider}\")\n811: ```\n812: \n813: ### Phase 9: 测试 (Day 8-10)\n814: \n815: 1. 单元测试\n816:    - 测试镜像准备逻辑\n817:    - 测试 AgentCube 提供商\n818:    - 测试 K8s 提供商\n819:    - 测试错误处理\n820: \n821: 2. 集成测试\n822:    - 测试完整的发布流程\n823:    - 测试与 Docker 集成\n824:    - 测试与 Kubernetes 集成\n825:    - 测试元数据更新\n826: \n827: 3. 端到端测试\n828:    - 测试 `pack` → `build` → `publish` 链路\n829:    - 测试 `publish` → `invoke` 链路\n830:    - 测试完整生命周期\n831: \n832: ### Phase 10: 文档 (Day 10)\n833: \n834: 1. 更新 CLI 文档\n835: 2. 添加使用示例\n836: 3. 添加故障排查指南\n837: 4. 更新 README\n838: \n839: ## Testing Strategy\n840: \n841: ### Unit Tests\n842: \n843: 1. **镜像准备测试**\n844:    - 测试本地镜像推送\n845:    - 测试云端镜像验证\n846:    - 测试镜像 URL 构建\n847: \n848: 2. **AgentCube 提供商测试**\n849:    - 测试 CR 创建\n850:    - 测试参数验证\n851:    - 测试错误处理\n852: \n853: 3. **K8s 提供商测试**\n854:    - 测试 Deployment 创建\n855:    - 测试 Service 创建\n856:    - 测试等待就绪逻辑\n857: \n858: 4. **错误处理测试**\n859:    - 测试输入验证\n860:    - 测试错误信息输出\n861:    - 测试日志记录\n862: \n863: ### Integration Tests\n864: \n865: 1. **Docker 集成测试**\n866:    - 测试真实镜像推送\n867:    - 测试凭证认证\n868:    - 测试镜像标记\n869: \n870: 2. **Kubernetes 集成测试**\n871:    - 测试真实 K8s 部署\n872:    - 测试 AgentRuntime CR\n873:    - 测试标准 K8s 资源\n874: \n875: 3. **完整流程测试**\n876:    - 测试 `pack` → `build` → `publish` 链路\n877:    - 测试 `publish` → `invoke` 链路\n878:    - 测试完整生命周期\n879: \n880: ### Test Coverage\n881: \n882: 目标：> 80% 代码覆盖率\n883: \n884: ## Configuration\n885: \n886: ### 命令行参数\n887: \n888: | 参数 | 类型 | 默认值 | 说明 |\n889: |------|------|--------|------|\n890: | `--workspace` / `-f` | str | `\".\"` | 工作空间路径 |\n891: | `--version` | str | `None` | 语义化版本号 |\n892: | `--image-url` | str | `None` | 镜像仓库 URL |\n893: | `--image-username` | str | `None` | 镜像仓库用户名 |\n894: | `--image-password` | str | `None` | 镜像仓库密码 |\n895: | `--description` | str | `None` | 代理描述 |\n896: | `--region` | str | `None` | 部署区域 |\n897: | `--cloud-provider` | str | `None` | 云服务提供商 |\n898: | `--provider` | str | `\"agentcube\"` | 目标提供商 |\n899: | `--node-port` | int | `None` | 节点端口 (30000-32767) |\n900: | `--replicas` | int | `None` | 副本数 |\n901: | `--namespace` | str | `None` | 命名空间 |\n902: | `--verbose` | bool | `False` | 详细日志 |\n903: \n904: ### 元数据配置\n905: \n906: 在 `agent_metadata.yaml` 中：\n907: \n908: ```yaml\n909: agent_name: \"my-agent\"\n910: version: \"1.0.0\"\n911: description: \"My AI agent\"\n912: language: \"python\"\n913: entrypoint: \"python main.py\"\n914: port: 8080\n915: build_mode: \"local\"  # 或 \"cloud\"\n916: \n917: # 镜像配置\n918: image:\n919:   name: \"my-agent\"\n920:   tag: \"1.0.0\"\n921: \n922: # 注册表配置（本地构建模式）\n923: registry_url: \"registry.example.com\"\n924: registry_username: \"admin\"\n925: registry_password: \"secret\"\n926: \n927: # AgentCube 提供商配置\n928: router_url: \"http://router.agentcube.svc.cluster.local:8080\"\n929: workload_manager_url: \"http://workload-manager.agentcube.svc.cluster.local:8080\"\n930: readiness_probe_path: \"/health\"\n931: readiness_probe_port: 8080\n932: \n933: # 部署信息（由 publish 命令更新）\n934: k8s_deployment:\n935:   type: \"AgentRuntime\"\n936:   namespace: \"default\"\n937:   agent_id: \"my-agent-abc123\"\n938:   agent_endpoint: \"http://my-agent.default.svc.cluster.local:8080\"\n939:   status: \"deployed\"\n940: ```\n941: \n942: ### 环境变量\n943: \n944: | 变量 | 说明 |\n945: |------|------|\n946: | `KUBECONFIG` | Kubernetes 配置文件路径 |\n947: | `DOCKER_HOST` | Docker 守护进程地址 |\n948: | `HTTP_PROXY` | HTTP 代理 |\n949: | `HTTPS_PROXY` | HTTPS 代理 |\n950: | `NO_PROXY` | 不使用代理的主机 |\n951: \n952: ## API Specification\n953: \n954: ### publish() 方法签名\n955: \n956: ```python\n957: def publish(\n958:     workspace_path: Path,\n959:     version: Optional[str] = None,\n960:     image_url: Optional[str] = None,\n961:     image_username: Optional[str] = None,\n962:     image_password: Optional[str] = None,\n963:     description: Optional[str] = None,\n964:     region: Optional[str] = None,\n965:     cloud_provider: Optional[str] = None,\n966:     provider: str = \"agentcube\",\n967:     node_port: Optional[int] = None,\n968:     replicas: Optional[int] = None,\n969:     namespace: Optional[str] = None,\n970:     verbose: bool = False\n971: ) -> Dict[str, Any]\n972: ```\n973: \n974: ### 返回值\n975: \n976: **AgentCube 提供商**：\n977: ```python\n978: {\n979:     \"agent_id\": \"my-agent-abc123\",\n980:     \"agent_endpoint\": \"http://my-agent.default.svc.cluster.local:8080\",\n981:     \"namespace\": \"default\",\n982:     \"agent_name\": \"my-agent\"\n983: }\n984: ```\n985: \n986: **K8s 提供商**：\n987: ```python\n988: {\n989:     \"deployment_name\": \"my-agent\",\n990:     \"service_name\": \"my-agent\",\n991:     \"namespace\": \"default\",\n992:     \"replicas\": 1,\n993:     \"container_port\": 8080,\n994:     \"node_port\": 30080,\n995:     \"service_url\": \"http://localhost:30080\",\n996:     \"agent_name\": \"my-agent\"\n997: }\n998: ```\n999: \n1000: ### 异常\n1001: \n1002: - `ValueError` - 无效的输入参数\n1003: - `RuntimeError` - Docker 不可用或部署失败\n1004: - `TimeoutError` - 部署超时\n1005: - `Exception` - 其他发布错误\n1006: \n1007: ## Security Considerations\n1008: \n1009: 1. **镜像凭证安全**\n1010:    - 支持安全的镜像注册表认证（HTTPS）\n1011:    - 避免在日志中输出凭证\n1012:    - 支持凭证轮换\n1013: \n1014: 2. **Kubernetes 访问安全**\n1015:    - 验证 kubeconfig 配置\n1016:    - 支持命名空间隔离\n1017:    - 遵循最小权限原则\n1018: \n1019: 3. **元数据安全**\n1020:    - 避免在元数据中存储敏感信息\n1021:    - 确保文件权限正确\n1022:    - 支持元数据加密（可选）\n1023: \n1024: 4. **部署安全**\n1025:    - 验证镜像来源\n1026:    - 支持镜像签名验证（可选）\n1027:    - 限制资源使用\n1028: \n1029: ## Performance Considerations\n1030: \n1031: 1. **镜像推送性能**\n1032:    - 支持镜像层缓存\n1033:    - 支持并行推送（可选）\n1034:    - 优化网络传输\n1035: \n1036: 2. **部署性能**\n1037:    - 利用 K8s 滚动更新\n1038:    - 支持并行资源创建\n1039:    - 优化健康检查\n1040: \n1041: 3. **资源使用**\n1042:    - 控制并发部署数\n1043:    - 支持资源限制\n1044:    - 优化内存使用\n1045: \n1046: ## Monitoring and Metrics\n1047: \n1048: ### 日志记录\n1049: \n1050: 使用 Python 标准库 `logging`：\n1051: \n1052: - 发布开始/结束\n1053: - 镜像准备进度\n1054: - 部署状态\n1055: - 错误信息\n1056: - 调试信息（verbose 模式）\n1057: \n1058: ### 发布指标\n1059: \n1060: - 发布时间\n1061: - 镜像推送时间\n1062: - 部署就绪时间\n1063: - 发布成功率\n1064: - 发布失败原因\n1065: \n1066: ## Open Questions\n1067: \n1068: 1. **Q1**: 是否需要支持多集群部署？\n1069:    - **当前**: 不支持\n1070:    - **讨论**: 支持同时部署到多个集群\n1071:    - **决策**: 初始不支持，后续根据需求添加\n1072: \n1073: 2. **Q2**: 是否需要支持金丝雀发布？\n1074:    - **当前**: 不支持\n1075:    - **讨论**: 支持金丝雀和蓝绿部署\n1076:    - **决策**: 初始不支持，后续根据需求添加\n1077: \n1078: 3. **Q3**: 是否需要支持自定义健康检查？\n1079:    - **当前**: 使用默认健康检查\n1080:    - **讨论**: 支持自定义健康检查配置\n1081:    - **决策**: 初始使用默认配置，后续扩展\n1082: \n1083: 4. **Q4**: 是否需要支持部署回滚？\n1084:    - **当前**: 不支持\n1085:    - **讨论**: 支持自动回滚和手动回滚\n1086:    - **决策**: 初始不支持，后续根据需求添加\n1087: \n1088: ## Next Steps\n1089: \n1090: 1. 创建 PublishRuntime 类\n1091: 2. 实现镜像准备功能\n1092: 3. 实现 AgentCube 提供商\n1093: 4. 实现 K8s 提供商\n1094: 5. 实现 CLI 命令集成\n1095: 6. 编写单元测试和集成测试\n1096: 7. 更新文档\n1097: 8. 集成到 CI/CD 流程\n1098: \n1099: ## References\n1100: \n1101: - [AgentCube CLI Design](../cli-toolkit/design.md)\n1102: - [AgentCube CLI Spec](../cli-toolkit/spec.md)\n1103: - [Kubernetes Python Client](https://github.com/kubernetes-client/python)\n1104: - [Docker SDK for Python](https://docker-py.readthedocs.io/)\n1105: - [Typer Documentation](https://typer.tiangolo.com/)\n\n(End of file - total 1105 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-022: CLI publish 命令\n\n## Overview\n\n实现 AgentCube CLI 的 `publish` 命令，用于将构建好的容器镜像发布到 Kubernetes 集群。该命令支持两种发布方式：AgentCube 自定义资源（AgentRuntime CR）和标准 Kubernetes 资源（Deployment + Service），能够处理镜像推送、资源部署和元数据更新。\n\n## Purpose\n\n提供 `kubectl-agentcube publish` 命令，实现：\n\n1. **镜像准备**：支持本地镜像推送到容器注册表，或使用云端构建的镜像 URL\n2. **AgentCube 提供商**：部署到 AgentRuntime 自定义资源，集成工作负载管理器和路由器\n3. **标准 K8s 提供商**：部署到标准的 Deployment 和 NodePort Service\n4. **版本管理**：支持语义化版本号，更新元数据中的部署信息\n5. **部署配置**：支持命名空间、副本数、节点端口等配置\n6. **状态验证**：等待部署就绪，提供详细的部署状态反馈\n\n## Module\n\n`cmd/cli` - AgentCube CLI 工具包","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775869112493,"end":1775869112502}}}}
{"type":"step_finish","timestamp":1775869112535,"sessionID":"ses_285f4a69fffebISu6m4ck4XKHy","part":{"id":"prt_d7a0c30b8001HPJWgyhtXtv4sw","reason":"tool-calls","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","messageID":"msg_d7a0c2601001snkuS1dTb1sCBV","sessionID":"ses_285f4a69fffebISu6m4ck4XKHy","type":"step-finish","tokens":{"total":37743,"input":522,"output":102,"reasoning":0,"cache":{"write":0,"read":37119}},"cost":0}}
{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775869116742,"sessionID":"ses_285f4a69fffebISu6m4ck4XKHy","part":{"id":"prt_d7a0c41430010QQIgb6nqXGh5N","messageID":"msg_d7a0c30ef001rbqQVEivX6oifx","sessionID":"ses_285f4a69fffebISu6m4ck4XKHy","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775869144257,"sessionID":"ses_285f4a69fffebISu6m4ck4XKHy","part":{"id":"prt_d7a0cac5c0010RmRRtRXUbNNGz","messageID":"msg_d7a0c30ef001rbqQVEivX6oifx","sessionID":"ses_285f4a69fffebISu6m4ck4XKHy","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-a92f0e6ed13d480c820236c3dee14544","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Proposal: AR-023 — CLI invoke/status 命令\n\n## Purpose\n\nThis proposal describes the implementation of the `invoke` and `status` commands for the AgentCube CLI (`kubectl-agentcube`). These commands enable users to:\n\n1. **`invoke`**: Send payloads to deployed agents via HTTP invocation endpoints, with support for custom headers and session management\n2. **`status`**: Query and display the current status of deployed agents in a formatted table\n\nThese commands complete the CLI's agent lifecycle management capabilities alongside the existing `pack`, `build`, and `publish` commands.\n\n## Scope\n\n### Invoke Command\n\nThe `invoke` command will provide:\n\n- **Payload submission**: POST JSON payloads to agent invocation endpoints\n- **Provider support**: Target both AgentCube CR (`agentcube`) and standard Kubernetes (`k8s`) deployments\n- **Custom headers**: Support for HTTP header customization via `--header` option\n- **Session management**: Automatic handling of `X-Agentcube-Session-Id` header for AgentRuntime deployments\n- **Error handling**: Validation for payload format and header syntax\n\n**Command signature**:\n```python\ndef invoke(\n    workspace: str = typer.Option(\".\", \"-f\", \"--workspace\"),\n    payload: str = typer.Option(\"{}\", \"--payload\"),\n    header_list: Optional[List[str]] = typer.Option(None, \"--header\"),\n    provider: str = typer.Option(\"agentcube\", \"--provider\"),\n    verbose: bool = typer.Option(False, \"--verbose\"),\n) -> None\n```\n\n### Status Command\n\nThe `status` command will provide:\n\n- **Status query**: Retrieve deployment status from Kubernetes or AgentCube provider\n- **Rich formatting**: Display status information in a formatted table\n- **Provider support**: Query both AgentRuntime CR and standard Kubernetes resources\n- **Exit codes**: Exit with code 1 for `not_published` or error states\n\n**Command signature**:\n```python\ndef status(\n    workspace: str = typer.Option(\".\", \"-f\", \"--workspace\"),\n    provider: str = typer.Option(\"agentcube\", \"--provider\"),\n    verbose: bool = typer.Option(False, \"--verbose\"),\n) -> None\n```\n\n### Implementation Components\n\n#### InvokeRuntime Class (`agentcube/runtime/invoke_runtime.py`)\n\n- `__init__(verbose, provider)`: Initialize runtime with provider configuration\n- `invoke(workspace_path, payload, headers)`: Main invocation entry point\n- `_validate_invoke_prerequisites(workspace_path)`: Validate agent is published and metadata exists\n- `_invoke_agent_via_agentcube(...)`: Invoke via AgentRuntime CR with session management\n- `_direct_http_invocation(...)`: Direct HTTP invocation for non-AgentCube providers\n\n#### StatusRuntime Class (`agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py`)\n\n- `__init__(verbose, provider)`: Initialize runtime with provider configuration\n- `get_status(workspace_path, provider)`: Retrieve agent status\n- `_get_k8s_status(metadata)`: Query standard Kubernetes Deployment/Service status\n- `_get_cr_k8s_status(metadata)`: Query AgentRuntime CR status\n\n### CLI Integration\n\nBoth commands will be integrated into the Typer app in `agentcube/cli/main.py`:\n\n```python\n@app.command()\ndef invoke(...) -> None:\n    ...\n\n@app.command()\ndef status(...) -> None:\n    ...\n```\n\n## Impact Analysis\n\n### Positive Impacts\n\n1. **Completes CLI lifecycle**: Users can now fully manage agents from development to execution\n2. **Testing workflow**: Enables end-to-end testing of deployed agents\n3. **Production monitoring**: Facilitates operational monitoring via status queries\n4. **Flexibility**: Support for multiple providers accommodates diverse deployment scenarios\n\n### Breaking Changes\n\nNone. These are new commands that do not modify existing functionality.\n\n### Dependencies\n\nThe implementation requires:\n\n- **Existing CLI dependencies**: `typer`, `pydantic`, `pyyaml`, `httpx`, `rich` (already in pyproject.toml)\n- **Kubernetes integration**: Optional `kubernetes>=28.0.0` for K8s provider support\n- **AgentCube provider**: Relies on client-go generated types (group `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`, version `v1alpha1`)\n\n### File Modifications\n\n1. **New files**:\n   - `agentcube/runtime/invoke_runtime.py`\n   - `agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py`\n\n2. **Modified files**:\n   - `agentcube/cli/main.py`: Add invoke and status command implementations\n   - `agentcube/runtime/__init__.py`: Export new runtime classes\n   - `agentcube/__init__.py`: Update exports (potentially include `StatusRuntime`)\n\n### Risk Assessment\n\n| Risk | Likelihood | Mitigation |\n|------|------------|------------|\n| UnboundLocalError in InvokeRuntime | High | Ensure response is always assigned before return in `_invoke_agent_via_agentcube` |\n| Header parsing errors | Medium | Strict validation with clear error messages |\n| Provider authentication issues | Medium | Leverage existing `AgentCubeProvider` and `KubernetesProvider` auth handling |\n| Status display inconsistencies | Low | Use Rich Table for consistent formatting |\n\n## Alternatives Considered\n\n### Alternative 1: Single combined command\n\n**Approach**: Combine invoke and status into a single `agent` command with subcommands (e.g., `agent invoke`, `agent status`)\n\n**Rejected because**:\n- Adds unnecessary nesting for two independent commands\n- Less discoverable than flat command structure\n- Inconsistent with existing `pack`, `build`, `publish` flat structure\n\n### Alternative 2: External HTTP client integration\n\n**Approach**: Rely entirely on external tools (curl, wget) for invocation and kubectl for status\n\n**Rejected because**:\n- Loses integration with CLI workspace context\n- Requires manual metadata management\n- No session header handling for AgentRuntime CR\n- Inconsistent user experience across commands\n\n### Alternative 3: Provider-specific commands\n\n**Approach**: Create separate commands per provider (e.g., `invoke-agentcube`, `invoke-k8s`)\n\n**Rejected because**:\n- Command explosion as providers grow\n- Duplicates validation and error handling logic\n- Provider selection via flag is more consistent with `publish` command\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n### Invoke Command\n\n- [ ] `kubectl-agentcube invoke --payload '{\"key\": \"value\"}'` successfully POSTs to agent endpoint\n- [ ] `--header` option accepts multiple headers in `key:value` format\n- [ ] Invalid JSON payload exits with code 1 and prints error message\n- [ ] Invalid header format exits with code 1 and prints expected format\n- [ ] Session ID header is automatically added for AgentRuntime deployments\n- [ ] Not-published agent exits with guidance to publish first\n- [ ] Verbose mode logs detailed HTTP request/response information\n\n### Status Command\n\n- [ ] Displays agent status in formatted Rich table with key fields\n- [ ] Exits with code 1 for `not_published` status\n- [ ] Exits with code 1 for error status\n- [ ] Successfully queries AgentRuntime CR status when provider is `agentcube`\n- [ ] Successfully queries K8s Deployment/Service status when provider is `k8s`\n- [ ] Verbose mode logs detailed status retrieval steps\n\n### Integration Tests\n\n- [ ] End-to-end test: pack → build → publish → invoke → status\n- [ ] Test invoke with both providers (`agentcube` and `k8s`)\n- [ ] Test status with both providers\n- [ ] Test error handling for unpublished agents\n- [ ] Test header parsing and transmission\n\n## Implementation Timeline\n\nEstimated effort: **5-7 days**\n\n| Phase | Duration | Deliverables |\n|-------|----------|--------------|\n| Phase 1: Runtime implementation | 2 days | `InvokeRuntime` and `StatusRuntime` classes |\n| Phase 2: CLI integration | 1 day | Typer command implementations in `main.py` |\n| Phase 3: Error handling and validation | 1 day | Payload/header validation, error messages |\n| Phase 4: Testing | 1-2 days | Unit tests, integration tests |\n| Phase 5: Documentation | 0.5 days | Command help text, examples |\n\n## References\n\n- CLI Toolkit Design: `cli-toolkit/design.md`\n- CLI Specification: `cli-toolkit/spec.md` (Requirements 487-519 for invoke, 509-519 for status)\n- AgentRuntime CR API: `deployment/client-go.md`\n- Python SDK (for reference HTTP patterns): `python-sdk/design.md`, `python-sdk/spec.md`","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/proposal.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/proposal.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775869144186,"end":1775869144255}}}}
